hree-inch%20euro%20top.%20%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20is%20made%20for%20people%20weighing%20between%20300%20and%20500%20pounds%2C%20so%20each%20design%20aspect%20supports%20heavy%20bodies.%20The%20foams%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20high-density%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20your%20mattress%20sagging.%20The%20coils%20are%20also%20made%20with%2014-gauge%20tempered%20recycled%20steel%2C%20a%20half-inch%20thicker%20and%20more%20durable%20than%20the%20coils%20in%20the%20Saatva%20Classic.%20The%20foam%20rails%20around%20the%20coils%20are%20six%20inches%20for%20extra%20edge%20support.%20With%20its%20intentional%20design%2C%20extra%20layers%2C%20and%20strong%20materials%2C%20the%20mattress%20can%20withstand%20a%20combined%20weight%20of%201%2C000%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saatva%20HD%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcertipur.us%2Fwhat-is-certified-foam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECertiPur-US%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ul.com%2Fservices%2Ful-greenguard-certification%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreenGuard%3C%2Fa%3E%20certified%2C%20which%20means%20it's%20made%20with%20safe%20foams%20and%20doesn't%20contain%20harmful%20pollutants.%20It's%20available%20in%20all%20standard%20sizes%2C%20plus%20full%2C%20split%20king%2C%20and%20California%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226cb40c8e-90aa-4fe4-ae3a-dd87a4705bcb%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%20of%20the%20Saatva%20HD%20Mattress%5C%22%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Saatva%20HD%20Mattress%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277a6ce2b-866f-4b57-ba6a-8a82a69b8a93%5C%22%3EDelivery%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESaatva%20offers%20free%20white%20glove%20delivery%20for%20all%20mattresses.%20The%20mattresses%20are%20made-to-order%2C%20and%20the%20lead%20time%20is%20about%20two%20weeks.%20Once%20the%20mattress%20was%20ready%20for%20delivery%2C%20I%20received%20a%20ca