ps%20and%20chest%20while%20cradling%20my%20waist.%20When%20lying%20on%20my%20stomach%20or%20back%2C%20I%20sink%20in%20just%20enough%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20without%20feeling%20stuck%20in%20the%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20exhibited%20excellent%20pressure%20relief%20and%20kept%20my%20spine%20aligned%2C%20as%20it%20nicely%20molded%20to%20my%20body.%20When%20using%20the%20Mattress%20Checker%20app%2C%20I%20only%20noticed%20a%20small%20curve%20in%20my%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20don't%20usually%20suffer%20from%20back%20pain%2C%20but%20I%20regularly%20go%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20which%20can%20sometimes%20make%20my%20body%20achy%20and%20sore.%20I%20never%20had%20trouble%20falling%20or%20staying%20asleep%2C%20even%20after%20a%20particularly%20tiring%20workout%2C%20or%20woke%20up%20with%20back%2C%20hip%2C%20or%20neck%20pain..%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20noticeable%20difference%20in%20my%20sleep%20quality%20when%20sleeping%20with%20the%20Saatva%20HD.%20I%20went%20out%20of%20town%20during%20the%20testing%20period%20and%20slept%20at%20a%20hotel.%20Before%20using%20the%20Saatva%20HD%2C%20I%20had%20never%20really%20noticed%20a%20real%20difference%20between%20my%20mattress%20at%20home%20and%20a%20hotel%20mattress.%20During%20this%20trip%2C%20though%2C%20I%20felt%20noticeably%20sorer%20and%20more%20tired%20the%20next%20day.%20I%20also%20woke%20up%20multiple%20times%20throughout%20the%20night%20trying%20to%20get%20into%20a%20comfortable%20position.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20I%20was%20ecstatic%20to%20return%20home%20and%20be%20reunited%20with%20my%20Saatva%20HD%20once%20our%20trip%20was%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22294b5629-7702-4ba4-a211-857181334ef6%5C%22%3EHeat%20dissipation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20uses%20an%20infrared%20thermometer%20to%20take%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20Saatva%20HD%20mattress.%20The%20thermometer%20reads%2073.5%20degree.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68307f1cc6ad288d1481c230%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20test%20heat%20dissipation%2C%20I%20take%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20mattress%20before%20going%20to%20bed%2C%20immediately%20after%20waking%20up%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20out%20of%20bed.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20heat%20dissipation%20keeps%20you%20cool%20overnight%20if%20you're%20a%20hot%20sleeper%20like%20me.%20To%20test%20heat%20dissipation%2C%20I%20took%20the%20mattress's%20temperature%20three%20times%20with%20an%20infrared%20thermometer%3A%20before%20lying%20down%2C%20immediately%20after%20waking%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20up.%20I%20repeated%20this%20process%20for%20three%20mornings%20and%20took%20the%20average%20of%20the%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20the%20mattress%20was%2072.8%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20before%20lying%20down%2C%2081%20degrees%20immediately%20after%20waking%20up%2C%20and%2074.5%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%20two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20out%20of%20bed.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20median%20temperature%20after%20getting%20up%20is%2089.5%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20so%20this%20mattress%20sleeps%20significantly%20cooler%20than%20other%20mattresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubjectively%2C%20I%20was%20comfortable%20using%20this%20mattress%20when%20testing.%20The%20mattress%20is%20not%20cool-to-the-touch%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cover%20is%20made%20of%20cotton%2C%20meaning%20it's%20naturally%20breathable%2C%20but%20it%20doesn't%20incorporate%20special%20cooling%20gels%20or%20materials%20to%20actively%20lower%20the%20surface%20temperature.%20I%20also%20never%20felt%20like%20I%20overheated%20at%20night.%20It's%20a%20good%20choice%20if%20you're%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20but%20I%20would%20pair%20it%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-sheets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooling%20sheets%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20you%20like%20a%20noticeably%20cool%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22df60d565-d5fd-4c4e-8bcb-eebb956f5afa%5C%22%3EEdge%20support%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20sits%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20Saatva%20HD%20while%20using%20a%20ruler%20to%20measure%20how%20far%20it%20sinks.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683080246ffb6822ec6155a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Saatva%20HD%20performed%20well%20in%20my%20edge%20support%20tests%2C%20only%20sinking%20about%203.5%20inches%20while%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20bed.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20support%20refers%20to%20how%20secure%20you%20feel%20lying%20or%20sitting%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20bed%2C%20and%20can%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20get%20in%20and%20out%20of%20bed%20or%20sit.%20It%20is%20particularly%20important%20if%20you%20sleep%20with%20another%20person%20to%20increase%20the%20usable%20surface%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20test%20edge%20support%2C%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20used%20a%20ruler%20to%20measure%20how%20far%20the%20mattress%20sank.%20I%20also%20slowly%20rolled%20off%20the%20side%20of%20the%20mattress%20to%20see%20how%20far%20I%20could%20go%20before%20falling%20off%20the%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saatva%20HD%20sank%203.5%20inches%20when%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20edge%2C%20which%20is%20average%20compared%20to%20other%20mattresses.%20For%20my%20second%20measure%2C%20I%20was%20almost%20parallel%20to%20the%20floor%20before%20I%20rolled%20off.%20In%20my%20experience%20using%20the%20bed%2C%20I%20had%20no%20problems%20with%20edge%20support.%20I%20always%20feel%20supported%20and%20stable%2C%20whether%20lying%20near%20the%20edge%20or%20sitting%20to%20put%20my%20socks%20on%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22625887cf-e616-4d4a-827a-61e7985ec842%5C%22%3EMotion%20isolation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soda%20can%20sits%20on%20the%20Saatva%20HD%20mattress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830808cc6ad288d1481c274%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETo%20test%20motion%20isolation%2C%20I%20dropped%20a%2020-pound%20weight%20on%20the%20mattress%20and%20observed%20if%20a%20soda%20can%20tipped%20over.%20I%20also%20used%20a%20vibrometer%20to%20detect%20any%20movement.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20motion%20isolation%20ensures%20you%20won't%20feel%20your%20sleep%20partner%20or%20pet's%20movements%20at%20night.%20To%20test%20motion%20isolation%2C%20I%20place%20a%20soda%20can%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20drop%20a%2020-pound%20weight%20six%20inches%20away%20from%20it%20five%20times%2C%20watching%20to%20see%20if%20it%20tips%20over.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20drop%20the%20weight%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20with%20a%20vibrometer%20placed%20on%20the%20other%20side%20and%20record%20the%20level%20of%20vibration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20was%20testing%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20with%20how%20the%20mattress%20absorbed%20movement.%20The%20soda%20can%20barely%20moved%20and%20never%20once%20tipped%20over.%20The%20vibrometer%20picked%20up%20low%20readings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubjectively%2C%20I%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%20Saatva%20HD's%20motion%20isolation.%20My%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20restless%20sleepers%2C%20and%20neither%20of%20us%20awoke%20at%20night%20because%20of%20the%20other's%20movements.%20We%20don't%20notice%20when%20our%20dog%20jumps%20on%20or%20off%20the%20bed%2C%20either.%20The%20Saatva%20HD's%20excellent%20edge%20support%20and%20motion%20isolation%20make%20it%20an%20excellent%20choice%20for%20cou