ier%20operating%20equipment%20at%20the%20Defense%20Information%20Systems%20Agency%20headquarters%20at%20Fort%20Meade%2C%20Maryland.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Abizaid%2FDefense%20Information%20Systems%20Agency%2FDVIDS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Defense%20Information%20Systems%20Agency%20is%20facing%20a%2010%25%20cut%20to%20its%20workforce%2C%20its%20director%20has%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDISA%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20tech%20arm%2C%20provides%20the%20military%20with%20IT%20and%20telecommunication%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20director%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bopportunity%20to%20ruthlessly%20realign.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Defense%20Information%20Systems%20Agency%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20IT%20arm%2C%20is%20facing%20a%2010%25%20cut%20to%20its%20workforce%2C%20its%20director%20told%20lawmakers%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20senators%20in%20Washington%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Lt.%20Gen.%20Paul%20Stanton%20said%20DISA%20was%20set%20to%20lose%20around%20one%20tenth%20of%20its%20staff%20but%20that%20that%20could%20be%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20giving%20us%20an%20opportunity%20to%20ruthlessly%20realign%20and%20optimize%20how%20we%20are%20addressing%20what%20is%20an%20evolving%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20doing%20a%20realignment%20and%20we're%20going%20back%20to%20the%20department%20to%20ask%20for%20what%20we%20refer%20to%20as%20a%20surgical%20rehiring.%20We%20need%20to%20hire%20the%20right%20people%20back%20into%20the%20right%20positions%20to%20then%20lead%20us%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDISA%20currently%20has%20around%2020%2C000%20employees%20%E2%80%94%20including%20about%206%2C800%20civilians%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20contractors%2C%20Stanton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cuts%20come%20as%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20realignment%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Defense%20Secretary%